Maintainer: <kjn0014@auburn.edu>
Description: 
    This R package implements supervised binary classification using numerical optimization. 
    It includes functions to estimate regression coefficients, compute bootstrap confidence intervals, 
    and generate confusion matrices with key metrics such as accuracy, sensitivity, and specificity.
